snippet.title: Emmy's Creative Corner
snippet.description:
A place where creative ideas are shared. 

Emmy R. Bennett is a published author who lives in Northern California with her husband, two children and their dog. She also has two adult children living out of state.
When she isn't at her desk writing, she's spending time with her family, gardening, crafting, or reading.
Emmy grew up in a Lutheran household. Although she's strong in her faith, she believes everyone has the right of free will, in their beliefs.
She loves to study genealogy and her family line has been traced back to the Vikings. It's one of the many inspirations from which she's drawn to write.
Check out my second channel Emmy Plays, below, where I stream video games.

snippet.title: Carrie Thompson
snippet.description:
I am a follower of Christ but not perfect. I'm a mother to my 5 yr old son whom I love with all my heart. I am a recovering addict from multiple substances but mostly 'opioids' & I've been clean for 6 yrs! I'm still finding my way, though, in this huge world so I keep my circle small b/c I have trust issues. 

My 'baby daddy' is in prison & hasn't wanted anything to do with us until he got a free tablet in prison. I have alot of reserves about him b/c he "loves us" when there's no one else to love him. I have a big love for Lana Del Rey's music. She has a rich, buttery voice with beautiful, well thought out lyrics. 

Besides my struggle, I want to make a difference in this world somehow & I believe I can do that by sharing my story. Someone can always get a 'one-up' on you but this is MY story & only I can tell it accurately.

snippet.title: Advanced Driving
snippet.description:
My name is James Stewart, an Advanced Driver with the Institute of Advanced Motorists (IAM)

My journey is a bit  different from most as I sat and passed the Advanced Driver test without having had any Advanced Car Lessons due to the Covid lockdown.

Prior to the test, I have had Advanced Rider training with the IAM a few years ago and was test ready, and have  had feedback to dashcam videos from an IAM Observer. 

I am now receiving lessons with the Edinburgh and the Borders advanced driving groups with the intention of resiting the test to get a 1st then training to become an Observer to train associates to an Advanced Level in both regions.

Hopefully my experiences will  be helpful to those considering and those undergoing Advanced Driver  training.

 

Car:           Mini Cooper S
Engine:     2.0  Litre Turbo 
Gearbox : Dual Clutch Transmission

snippet.title: JekyllHydeClub
snippet.description:
We're legally blind, criminally strange, and sometimes funny.
 
Other than our local Southern OR Spooky variety t.v show, Frightfully Brilliant, our other claim to fame is having Slappy from Goosebumps as our roommate. Oh yeah and being the only legally blind spooky youtubers.
 
 Come into the darkness with us, for everyone knows the Spooky Stars only come out at night. Being legally blind, and doing our own filming, we give a whole new meaning to the concept of "darkly inclined'. On this channel you will be exposed to our true tales of the uncanny + very awesometastic diy ideas that you're sure to love as well as frightful product reviews of all the spooky items we shop for. 

We always find the most interesting items at the best prices that won't break your bank account for bank accounts have feelings to. Our interests range from spooky tarot, books and movies to spooky decor, clothing, jewelry and collectable toys. We are Morticia and Gomez, our channel masscott is Slappy.

snippet.title: John Medeiros
snippet.description: These songs were not recorded in a studio. These songs were all recorded at home, using my laptop your support is appreciated. When i was younger i was asked if i like to join to make a band with my brother & his friends, In the 80s for us to play at family bars & weddings then the DJ era came & we decided to quit. But i kept on playing for fun through the years i started making up my own little tunes in the 90s after in 2010 i got my 1st laptop & after found a way to do recordings with layers adding drums & keyboard. Until now i kept making Original music & more Thank you so much for watching. I'm the composer of all my Original music

snippet.title: Western Australia Now and Then
snippet.description:
Western Australia Now and Then is your gateway to Western Australia.

Towns, cities, interesting places, wildlife, wildflowers, folklore, mysteries, haunted places, campsites, 4x4 and motorhome adventures, you name it, we have it here or on our main website www.wanowandthen.com

Join us as we travel around this huge state and see what we see. We will also share information about the gear we use, things
we cook on the road, the best places to see and camp and give you a look at the vehicles we use to get about.

I hope you find something here that you find interesting and fun.

snippet.title: Raven Keefer
snippet.description:
Time to Think, other playlists just graze surface. If you want reality, the unfiltered, unobscured then the playlists are for you. Agree, or don't, but try not to let beliefs get in the way of truth.
If you look with the result of your search already planted in fenced in beliefs you were educated, indoctrinated to accept, you'll find nothing.
We are beings far removed from the flesh we occupy. Our power is in our ability to manifest the world we want. It's why everything divisive, deceitful, dark, fear mongering, anxiety producing, and world ending is all you get on TV, in movies, science programming, magazines, and music. If you believe it, it becomes so. If enough dwell on it, everywhere becomes what you're feeding on.
What are you feeding on, then spreading into the world? The hate, deceit, division or would you like to try something new?
Those "deleted video" slots? Censorship! You shouldn't tolerate it. Free speech doesn't mean we agree except on the right to speak

snippet.title: Scribblebytes
snippet.description:
How To Pretend To Be Fine.

+Bachelor of Arts, Motion Picture Medium from the only Academy-Award¬Æ 
winning college on the African continent.

We are not fine, but we pretend we are.  Why? That's what Scribblebytes is for...to find out.

||This channel is for educational and research purposes in the areas of Screen Acting, Character Semiotics and (F)ego DNA Schemas. After 13 months of ethnographic field research into the target audience, the collected data has been translated into 3 distinct characters:

1. Charlie Manner, the Magician archetype

2. Rebble Pebble, the Maverick archetype

3. Mvikeli, the Innocent archetype.
 

With the YouTube community's interaction, this project continues to develop.||

NB: The views expressed by the fictional characters featured on this channel do not represent the views of Scribblebytes or its associates. This channel is a presentation of academic Character Study and should be viewed as such.

snippet.title: ClownyIsAName
snippet.description:
Heyo! I'm Clowny, call me Clown, Clowny, whatever. I'm Genderfluid, so any pronouns could work for me!
I'm not too common with Youtube, although I do Twitch!
What games I commonly play:
Roblox for horror games, or just overall fun! (Specific horror games, The Mimic!)
Minecraft is mostly going to be posted on this Channel!
Any other games that I could find later on, but steam is odd for me, and I have no money- And I'm still getting adjusted.
I go on frequent breaks here and there, but I'm working on it!
For Spanish Speakers, Yo hablo un poco espanol, hola! Como estas?
For Dutch Speakers, Hallo! Ik spreekt beetje nederlands!
And just to let you know, my computer isn't always the best- And there will be glitches and annoying bits, or testing out new stuff- My editing systems as well are not at all great, but I'm still trying! And I'm hoping to bring you along the way.
I play whatever makes me feel best, although polite criticism and recommendations will be appreciated! Best of wishes:)

snippet.title: Dreama Collins
snippet.description:
When I began this channel it was meant to be narcissistic survivors and/or those wanting information about narcissism. I will leave those videos up, however; I have found that there are other things I'd like to talk about or share with  you. So, in addition to sharing my experience and knowledge of narcissism with you, I will be sharing my poems, music and other things. You could say my channel is very eclectic, maybe a little something for everyone. It might sound really corny but I kinda owe this change to Johnny Depp. Some of the words he's imparted to his fans have made me try to be a bit braver in sharing. For better or worse I hope you will subscribe and share my channel, thank you!

snippet.title: Nick Angelo
snippet.description:
Human life is an anomaly, and your distinct consciousness is equivalent to hitting a lottery of infinite proportions. Even a split second change before we were conceived could've resulted in someone else existing, somewhat like a sibling, altering the future infinitely. Everything that ever happened before your creation had a significant influence on your individual existence. 

 We've manifested as the greatest lifeforms of all time on our planet and in our solar system. We're lucky to live in a great country and exist in this privileged era of technological/medical advances over our primitive ancestors. Appreciate it while you can.

 I hold a moral code, but I believe bibles are fairy tales. Churches are cults. I don't deny miracles exist, I realize life IS the miracle happening right in front of me. Life is real magic every day. Our actions are what live on after death because every one of our actions will impact the future. It's called the butterfly effect.

 Woke SJW's, fuck off.

snippet.title: Wendy H
snippet.description:
I‚Äôm 50+ year old Albertan woman living, laughing and loving the journey through life with my soulmate Chris, and we‚Äôre just starting to homestead here in Canada. We have a blended family of seven, who have all grown and flown the nest and are extremely proud grandparents to 5 beautiful grandchildren. We share our lives with three dogs, a female working/field English Springer Spaniel named ‚ÄúGhia‚Äù, a crazy little female terrier x rescue named ‚ÄúSassy‚Äù, and the gentle giant, a female Black Lab/Great Pyrenees x rescue named ‚ÄúPudge‚Äù. We often foster dogs for various rescues and I greatly enjoy doing dog sports like agility, dock diving, UpDog, etc with our fuzzy crew.

snippet.title: Ivan Ivo Martinetti
snippet.description:
Being a Manifesting Generator (Human Design) I find it impossible to focus on one thing. I cannot even predict what I am going to do tomorrow, never mind predicting what this channel is going to be about, we just have to do it and see where the journey takes us. I use music to express myself and bring joy to others. 

Please let me know if you agree with the music school and others who rejected my musical abilities? Should I continue making music or you agree that it is absolutely horrible and I should sell my guitar?

Recently I came across couple of my old hard drives and cassette tapes that contained hundreds of my original songs that I never got to record. Unfortunately recording and making videos is costly. Ths was the bases of me starting this channel, I wanted to see if I can find enough people out there who like my music creations and are willing to support the project financially.

Channel started in July 2021

snippet.description: Blue, bluer, and yet bluer, still. The ocean is a vast, deep place, but our minds are greater, and like the ocean, we have only acquired an inkling of the miraculous and frightening depths that are our own minds. Seek the truth, entertain the impossible, and never become idle of your unique human beauty. There are monsters in this world, and they live within us, lurking in the shadows of our subconscious, like a slithering, voracious sea creature, and only once we become aware of the evils that reside within ourselves may we then strive to conquer our demons and achieve betterment of ourselves, and of our world.

snippet.title: Climate Change Poems
snippet.description:
The Climate Change Channel is to Raise Awareness of Climate Change and how each one of us can make a difference. There will be ongoing voice over videos (some poems) with images rather than one of those boring lectures you may have seen! Basically, our environment is important for our survival as well as future generations to have the same opportunities as we presently enjoy. Our population is increasing at a rapid rate, and sharing awareness as we progress together into the 21st century is something worth sharing. 

Videos will be based around how we as humans relate to planet earth (and the solar system) from rivers and streams to trees and bees, and how we depend on these natural resources to sustain life; and to 'spark your thoughts' on various topics in the comments section. Our planet is a once in a lifetime experience, so let's look after it! :) What are your favourite topics of living on this planet? Please feel free to subscribe and keep the channel alive! Enjoy.

Our population is increasing at a rapid rate, and sharing awareness as we progress together into the 21st century is something worth sharing. 

Videos will be based around how we as humans relate to planet earth (and the solar system) from rivers and streams to trees and bees, and how we depend on these natural resources to sustain life; and to 'spark your thoughts' on various topics in the comments section. Our planet is a once in a lifetime experience, so let's look after it! :) What are your favourite topics of living on this planet? Please feel free to subscribe and keep the channel alive! Enjoy.

snippet.title: Annie
snippet.description:
Hey!  Nice of you to pop by! 
This is simply an alternative, TEMPORARY Channel, until I get my hacked PC renewed, and can resume with my original  annie46664  channel with 2k+ subs.  
BTW: 46664 was Nelson Mandela's prison cell number, chosen out of much respect for such an incredible man whom I consider one of my many heroes, and has zilch to do with any Satanism. 
I'm flattered to have any Subs here though!  THANK YOU GUYS!
I'm PROUDLY South African and live in DURBAN on the East Coast of SA, where I was also born and raised, but I do have Swiss Nationality as well ... having married a Swiss French gent back in the mid 1980's.  I lived in Zurich for 6 years and our only son was born in Horgen ZH ... but my Swiss family are from Gruyere in the French speaking Canton of Fribourg.
The only language that I've mastered, is ENGLISH.  My Afrikaans, Zulu, French and German ALL SUCK!
I'm passionate about a LOT of things ... but namely, humanitarian causes, Wildlife, integrity and HONESTY!

snippet.title: Ani Ore
snippet.description: Hi ~ Im Ani from Oregon ~ Im interested in creating Tiny Villages ~ each year I focus on a theme ~ and enjoy the build from the ground up literally.  I collect Lemax Spooky Town, Lemax other buildings, Department 56, O Scale Trains, Lionel, Fastrack, O Scale buildings. I repurpose Toys that are in the right scale. ~ I learn a lot from the Train modeler's and DM Game board and Terrain artists.  I use found objects, Goodwill, purchased products like Woodland Scenics and currently in love with the Gamer's products. I've only just started ... learn more each year ~ love the community of likewise artists, collectors and hobbyist :D

snippet.title: Pamela Jackson
snippet.description:
I'm often called a girly girl, and I'm often called a Tomboy, because I have an open mind when it comes to most things and I'm usually willing to try anything at least once. Even if I am doing something that might often be traditionally thought of as an activity that men prefer over women, I still like to look nice & feminine while doing so. I'm a huge fan of college football and I love my Tennessee Volunteers. I like camping, swimming, fishing, boating, target practice and many other outdoor activities. At the same time, I LOVE all things beauty and I'm always open to trying new products. I love my skin care products, all make up products, hair products, you name it. Follow me on Instagram: @gunsnglitter69 
#bleedorange #vol4life #VolNation Very proud to come from a #VolsFamily
